26:03.500 --> 26:08.960
It's a long story. Part 23. The Loch Ness Monster.

26:10.500 --> 26:13.640
Loch Ness is in a mincely deep lake in the

26:13.640 --> 26:15.160
northeastern Highlands of Scotland.

26:16.460 --> 26:19.740
It is overlooked by booed in hills and wild moorland,

26:20.520 --> 26:23.280
